	<name>TuxScape</name>
	<summary>A mythical adventure as Tux!</summary>
	<description>
		<p>Inspired by the famous game Run-Escape.</p>
		<p>All your stats are shown in the title bar. ;)</p>
		<p>Mouse locks when you click on the window, press ESCAPE to unlock the mouse.</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Left Click = Attack</li>
			<li>Right Click = Target Weapon / Engage Jet Pack</li>
			<li>W,A,S,D / Arrow Keys = Move</li>
			<li>L-SHIFT / R-CTRL = Sprint/Fast</li>
			<li>Space = Jet Pack</li>
			<li>1-9 = Weapon Change</li>
			<li>C = Toggle between First and Third person</li>
			<li>V / MOUSE4 = Toggle between stickey/toggle mouse clicks (good for afk)</li>
		</ul>
	</description>
